Package: ramcmc
Title: Robust Adaptive Metropolis Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jouni Helske
Maintainer: Jouni Helske <jouni.helske@jyu.fi>
Description: Fast Cholesky update and downdate functions, 
    and function for updating the covariance matrix of the proposal 
    distribution as specified in robust adaptive Metropolis algorithm 
    by Vihola (2012). These functions can be used directly from R or 
    the corresponding C++ header files can be linked to other R packages.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.8)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
